Usage: report_property [-help] [-property_list <list of properties>]
                       [> <file_name>] [>> <file_name>] {<collection> | <list_of_collections>}

-help                                   # Prints out the command usage
<collection>                            # Specifies the list of collections
                                        # (string, optional)
<list_of_collections>                   # Specifies the list of collections
                                        # (string, optional)
-property_list <list of properties>     # List of valid property names
                                        # (string, optional)
> <file_name>                           # Redirect output to file
                                        # (redirect_operator, optional)
>> <file_name>                          # Redirect output to file
                                        # (redirect_operator, optional)